<item>
            <title>[STORM-2950] ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException in FieldsGrouper.chooseTasks function</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STORM-2950</link>
                <project id="12314820" key="STORM">Apache Storm</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;TupleUtils.chooseTaskIndex:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;T&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; chooseTaskIndex(List&amp;lt;T&amp;gt; keys, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; numTasks) {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Math&lt;/span&gt;.abs(listHashCode(keys)) % numTasks;
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160; &lt;br/&gt;
listHashCode(keys) might return Integer.MIN_VALUE (-2147483648).   Math.abs(-2147483648) equals to  -2147483648. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In this case, chooseTaskIndex might return negative numbers and it will cause ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException in FieldsGrouper.chooseTasks&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
 @Override
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; List&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Integer&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; chooseTasks(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; taskId, List&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; values) {
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; targetTaskIndex = TupleUtils.chooseTaskIndex(outFields.select(groupFields, values), numTasks);
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; targetTasks.get(targetTaskIndex);
        }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
